        }

        package "Emulated (11 backends)" as br_emu #FFECB3 {
                component "emulated_barrier.inl" as br_inl #FFE082
                note bottom of br_inl
                    **Mutex + condvar + generation counter**
                    ───────────────────────────────────────
                    • Fixed-size barrier object pool
                    • count/current/generation state
                    • Last arriver releases all waiters
                    • No heap allocation at runtime
                    • Gives every backend portable rendezvous semantics
                end note

